HEADWORD: Cocainism
<hw>Co*ca"in*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A morbid condition produced by the habitual and excessive use of
cocaine.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Co*ca"in*ist</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
